    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min on each sides</p><p>Add a couple of splashes of <strong>water</strong> to the pan and cover with a lid</p><p>Cook for a further 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
